  <scopecontent id="aspace_8dfe79056928f106b91f9c29827dc864">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>Collection contains Cornell University memorabilia and ephemera. Items include bookends, clocks, souvenirs, and other branded items. For college or department-specific memorabilia, please refer to those collections.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <separatedmaterial id="aspace_e12af0b53a946b28e6f19a38d470339c">
    <head>Separated Materials</head>
<p>For glassware, dinnerware, and ceramics, see collection #41-7-1964, Cornell University ceramics, glassware, and metalware collection.</p><p>For clothing and textiles, see collection #47-7-3439, Cornell University banners, clothing, and other textiles.</p><p>For silver and jewelry, see collection #47-7-4580, Cornell University tableware, cutlery, and silver collection.</p>  </separatedmaterial>
